data.description: 1ST FLOOR Charmer, in the predominately ALL AGE community of PLATINA. BRIGHT and AIRY unit with RENOVATED kitchen and bathrooms. Tiles are neutral and most furniture will remain if wanted! A/C approx. 5 Years New. Walk out your front door and view the beautiful water views and nature at its best.  This 1st floor unit includes a personal locked storage area, great for bikes & beach chairs. Alexandra Village is one of the only villages that allows non-commercial trucks to park overnight in selected areas.
